	    <problem-set>
	      <header>
		<para>Write the conjugate base for:</para>
	      </header>
	      <entry>
		<shortcode>Shortcode</shortcode>
		<problem>
		  <para><chem_compound>H_{2}CO_{3}</chem_compound></para>
		</problem>
		<solution>
		  <para>This is an acid. A proton needs to be donated to form the conjugate base:</para>
		  <para><chem_compound>H_{2}CO_{3}</chem_compound> <latex>\to</latex> <chem_compound>HCO_{3}^{-} + H^{+}</chem_compound></para>
		  <para><correct><chem_compound>HCO_{3}^{-}</chem_compound></correct> is the conjugate base of <chem_compound>H_{2}CO_{3}</chem_compound>.</para>
