		  <para><unit_number><number>27</number><unit>g</unit></unit_number> of sodium bicarbonate (<chem_compound>NaHCO_{3}</chem_compound>) added to <unit_number><number>22.6</number><unit>cm<sup>3</sup></unit></unit_number> of water.</para>
