		  <para>V = <unit_number><number>12.76</number><unit>cm<sup>3</sup></unit></unit_number> <latex>\times \dfrac{<number>0.001</number> {\text{ dm}}^{3}}{<number>1</number> {\text{ cm}}^{3}}</latex> = <unit_number><number>0.01276</number><unit>dm<sup>3</sup></unit></unit_number></para>
		  <para>C(<chem_compound>HCl</chem_compound>) = <latex>\dfrac{\text{n (mol)}}{\text{V (dm}^{3}{\text{)}}} = \dfrac{<number><coeff>9.0</coeff><exp>-4</exp></number> {\text{ mol}}}{<number>0.01276</number> {\text{ dm}}^{3}}</latex> = <correct><unit_number><number>0.07</number><unit>mol.dm<sup>-3</sup></unit></unit_number></correct></para>
