    </image>
    <caption>
      <para>The main amino acid found in keratin: <emphasis effect="bold">cystine</emphasis>.</para>
    </caption>
  </figure>
  <para>Amino acids are composed of an amine group (Figure <link target-id="fig:acidsandbases:aminoacid"/> (a)) and a carboxylic acid group (Figure <link target-id="fig:acidsandbases:aminoacid"/> (b)) connected by a carbon chain.</para>
  <figure id="fig:acidsandbases:aminoacid">
