	  <shortcode>00zm</shortcode>
	  <header>
	    <para>The compound <chem_compound>NaHCO_{3}</chem_compound> is commonly known as baking soda. A recipe requires <unit_number><number>1.6</number><unit>g</unit></unit_number> of baking soda, mixed with other ingredients, to bake a cake.</para>
	  </header>
