	      <para>M(<chem_compound>NaHCO_{3}</chem_compound>) = <number>23.0</number> + <number>1.01</number> + <number>12.0</number> + (<number>3</number> x <number>16.0</number>) = <unit_number><number>84.01</number><unit>g.mol<sup>-1</sup></unit></unit_number></para>
